WEBVTT

00:16:00.386 --> 00:16:04.732
Možemo ovo postići samo ako prvo priznamo

00:16:05.347 --> 00:16:07.990
da smo zapostavili jedni druge.

00:16:09.971 --> 00:16:13.185
Ako još ima nade za okupljanjem

00:16:13.930 --> 00:16:15.280
u ovom zloslutnom času,

00:16:16.202 --> 00:16:17.393
u ovome je.

00:16:18.870 --> 00:16:20.572
Predugo smo

00:16:21.547 --> 00:16:24.916
jurili razne bleštave snove

00:16:25.818 --> 00:16:31.682
po ceni privrženosti
temeljnom snu o zajedništvu,